  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321600/extras/7cd62774626ef4b57c460d636f65a2ba.webp?t=1734532653\" width=314 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In all game modes you have to slide through the labyrinth with your cube.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>in Classic Mode: </strong><i>Collect all the items you can reach and don't lose any lives.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>in Time Mode: </strong>Collect all reachable items as quickly as possible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>in Runes Mode: </strong><i>Collect all accessible objects and, if necessary, use the appropriate rune to slide through the rune gates.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321600/extras/1bf4a3c3f998696508a8d04082eeccac.webp?t=1734532653\" width=314 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Currently 80 Labyrinth-Maps</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 different kind of Traps</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Customizing</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Day and Night-Cycle (Real Time, related on Map or permanently chosen Daytime)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levelsystem</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321600/extras/541aec0cac84065411a6827e8688